---
import "./Approach.css";
---
<section class="kitchen-hero">
    <!-- Top Images Row -->
    <div class="kitchen-hero__top-images">
        <img src="/KitchenPage/kitchen1.png" alt="Modern Kitchen 1" />
        <img src="/KitchenPage/kitchen2.png" alt="Modern Kitchen 2" />
    </div>
    <!-- Content Row (Text + Side Image, aligned as in the reference) -->
    <div class="kitchen-hero__content-row">
        <div class="kitchen-hero__text">
            <h1>
                Custom Kitchen <br />
                Remodeling in <br />
                Maryland
            </h1>
            <p>
                Upgrade the heart of your home with a kitchen that blends style, function, and lasting value.<br />
                We specialize in custom kitchen remodeling across Maryland, transforming outdated kitchens into modern, functional, and beautiful spaces.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether you're dreaming of new cabinets, quartz countertops, smart lighting, or a full layout transformation — we bring craftsmanship and care to every detail.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Proudly serving Rosedale, Towson, Glen Burnie, Baltimore, Bethesda, Gaithersburg, Germantown, and all of Montgomery County.</li>
                <li>Request your free quote today and let’s bring your kitchen vision to life.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Serving Montgomery County with trusted kitchen remodeling solutions — contact Bethelor today to get started.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="kitchen-hero__cta">
                Request your free quote →
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="kitchen-hero__side-image">
            <img src="/KitchenPage/kitchen3.png" alt="Custom Kitchen Design" />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>